{"tid":457071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"她曾是紅極一時的AV女優，引退後努力追夢，轉型成為樂隊主音！","createTime":"2017-11-03T13:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T13:32:28.000Z","uid":49163,"like":214,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8f8082a3d0af03fa1d7efec4c8ba4940a4aa22","tid":457071,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-preview-jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-preview-jpg.jpg&h=d36d3297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAV女優要轉型本身已經不是易事，當中的成功例子更佔少數，但成瀨心美可說是數一數二的代表。<br />\n<br />\n現年28歲的成瀨心美，2008年以AV女優身份出道，用過「ここみ、KOKOMI、渡辺恵美」等藝名。成瀨心美樣子可愛甜美，身材火辣，迅速在AV界竄紅，幾年間已拍下過百部AV作品，也拿下不少AV界的獎項。打滾短短數年，成瀨心美在2012年以考慮到健康狀況轉差為由，不再接拍AV作品，到了2013年更正式宣佈引退。<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-9.jpg&h=cab430de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-11.jpg&h=a0cd8ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-12.jpg&h=2e428942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n引退後的成瀨心美變得低調，有關她的去向更是謠言滿天飛。有時傳出她在夜店做小姐，有時則傳出她轉職賣街頭小食。<br />\n<br />\n原來，成瀨心美以「cocomi」的名義，組成搖滾樂隊「mezcolanza」（メスコランサ）。上週，樂隊在東京「涉谷LUSH」Live House舉行演唱會，吸引數百名樂迷入場支持。樂隊包括五名成員，有男有女，歌曲搖滾輕快，其中一首《Dream Wonderland》更是引起全場掌聲雷動，氣氛熱烈。<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-8.jpg&h=061e3040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-10.jpg&h=6c678e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂隊當中，成瀨心美擔任主音唱歌，更會自己寫歌填詞，可謂全能的唱作歌手。初時，她將唱歌的片段發放上網，美妙的歌喉震驚聽眾，更被認為可媲美天后西野加奈，也令你完全不會聯想到她曾是AV女優。<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-2.jpg&h=97de2c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-3.jpg&h=5b742c16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-4.jpg&h=51b1250f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/naruse-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnaruse-5.jpg&h=9d1b2591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成瀨心美倒沒有掩飾自己曾是AV女優的身份，她依然沿用真名在網上與觀眾互動。其實，她喜歡唱歌不是最近的事，她曾參加過AKB48的選秀，可惜沒有入圍。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，自己拍攝AV期間，也沒有遺忘自己當歌手的夢想。現在她追夢成功，獲得家人、朋友和大量樂迷的愛戴，令她在演唱會上也不禁大叫「好幸福」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=286&amp;v=LWWgVT_vKEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D286%26v%3DLWWgVT_vKEA&d=Vpzl80cSJ24bKsJFav%2BswnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9ecc47e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=286&amp;v=LWWgVT_vKEA</a><br />\n<br />\n來源:<a href=\"http://www.addoil.com/men/330233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.addoil.com%2Fmen%2F330233&d=Vpzl80cSJ24bKsJFav%2BswnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=68ff28df\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.addoil.com/men/330233</a>"},{"pid":"f29d280b4dfbcdb64532f3bd8127d7e879a38880","tid":457071,"uid":2419,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"美心瀨粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b12ee0265f9114c1cb96d28b1a263121f64abe6","tid":457071,"uid":49163,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"估唔到又唱得幾好喎衰鬼"},{"pid":"d16b94ce4f3d2af12c0e59da38714b3f1a7b76f0","tid":457071,"uid":70988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba420ac295e530704d71b302fe8a217004cee069","tid":457071,"uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美心瀨粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0dffcd8458d5690bc2f7b275461624991932a1a","tid":457071,"uid":44333,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"等睇整容前"},{"pid":"f3a02c98d50244ae11dea82e2b0c2273de3fdd21","tid":457071,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到又唱得幾好喎衰鬼</blockquote><br />\n屌<br />\n仲好聽過佢春叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.